Package com.geodesk.feature.match

Class Selector

java.lang.Object
com.clarisma.common.ast.Ast
com.clarisma.common.ast.Expression
com.geodesk.feature.match.Selector
public class Selector extends Expression
A class that represents a parsed GOQL selector expression (e.g. "na[amenity=restaurant][cuisine=pizza]") A Selector can have zero or more TagClauses, which are arranged in table-scan order.

      public static final int CLAUSE_LOCAL_REQUIRED
      The types of clauses that are present in this Selector: local/global, required/optional. A required-key clause only matches if its key is present; an optional-key clause can match even if the key is missing (e.g. [!key], [key!=abc])
